<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-83-1057 </DOCNO><TEXT>Documentation is provided in this report for the closeout of IE Bulletin80-23 regarding failures in safety-related systems of nuclear power plantsdue to solenoid valves manufactured by the Valcor Engineering Corporation.Closeout is based on the implementation and verification of three actionsby licensees of operating plants, or one action by holders of constructionpermits. Evaluation of utility responses and NRC/Region inspection reportsindicates that the bulletin is closed out for all of the 120 facilitiesto which it was issued for action. Background information is suppliedin the Introduction and Appendix A of this report.</TEXT></DOC>